item.content:encoded:
Supermarket Manager Simulator is a business game. Play as the store manager in this game and stock up on a variety of goods, from chips and fries to meats, burgers, vegetables, and fruits. From stocking, and shelving to selling, you will be the one to take care of it! When havingenough money, you can expand your store!

item.content:encoded:
My Perfect Hotel is a fun casual business simulation game. You are a hotel tycoon, responsible for the management of a five-star hotel. Your goal is to make your hotel the best hotel in the world. It is not an easy task to manage the entire hotel. From the construction of the hotel to the toilet paper in the toilet, you need to arrange everything.
